# Open House Market Place (this repo)

## Read first

- **[AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md)** — where to look before substantive edits.
- **[docs/soul.md](docs/soul.md)** — brand voice, Dr. Jan Duffy (**never "Janet"**), NAP, audience.
- **[docs/skill.md](docs/skill.md)** — stack, integrations, file map, perf/CSP notes.
- **[docs/klb-vercel-playbook.md](docs/klb-vercel-playbook.md)** — Vercel, env, CSP maintenance.

## Single source of truth

- **NAP / GBP / hours / service area:** [`config/gbp.ts`](config/gbp.ts) — do not duplicate conflicting phone or address elsewhere without updating this file.

## Hard boundaries

- **`components/idx/*`:** Do **not** modify unless the product owner explicitly approves (MLS/IDX compliance).
- **RealScout CSP:** Both `em.realscout.com` and `www.realscout.com` belong in `script-src` and `connect-src` when touching [`lib/csp-header.mjs`](lib/csp-header.mjs).

## Stack reminder

- Next.js 15 **App Router** (`app/`), not Pages Router (`getStaticProps` / `getServerSideProps`).
- Prefer **server components**; client only for interactivity. Dynamic route params: **`params: Promise<...>`** where applicable.

## Deploy

- Prefer **`vercel build`** for production checks; Cloudflare **DNS-only** (gray cloud) with Vercel — no orange-cloud proxy.
- **Production only:** use **`vercel deploy --prod`** (never preview). Vercel Git auto-builds **`main`** only; see [docs/VERCEL_DEPLOYMENT.md](docs/VERCEL_DEPLOYMENT.md).
